140
00:08:16.356 --> 00:08:19.956
So the EV field, as in the

141
00:08:19.976 --> 00:08:23.436
International Society for Extracellular Vesicles, has taken this very

142
00:08:23.476 --> 00:08:27.456
pragmatic approach of classifying these vesicles based on

143
00:08:27.496 --> 00:08:31.206
