186
00:11:05.936 --> 00:11:09.416
extracellular vesicles have emerged as important

187
00:11:09.476 --> 00:11:13.436
mediators of intercellular communication in the tumor microenvironment.

188
00:11:13.896 --> 00:11:17.536
They may also be released into the bloodstream, into body fluids,

189
00:11:18.516 --> 00:11:22.476
and have systemic effects and educate the

190
00:11:22.716 --> 00:11:26.156
pre-metastatic niches so eloquently shown by David Liden's lab,

191
00:11:26.656 --> 00:11:28.956
and like he just alluded to.

192
00:11:31.316 --> 00:11:35.256
So these extracellular vesicles can bring about the

193
00:11:35.276 --> 00:11:39.236
horizontal transfer of cargo, in the tumor microenvironment and bring

194
00:11:39.276 --> 00:11:42.916
