308
00:18:14.272 --> 00:18:16.572
And so these endosomes function as

309
00:18:16.752 --> 00:18:20.672
reserves for the protease, and it's available

310
00:18:21.572 --> 00:18:25.232
as needed depending upon when the tumor cell need to

311
00:18:25.552 --> 00:18:29.516
shed these vesicles for degradation.Okay, so these TMVs also

