00:20:12.276 --> 00:20:16.226
AF6 from these TMVs

341
00:20:16.256 --> 00:20:18.856
that were released. So

342
00:20:19.896 --> 00:20:23.696
this is our working hypothesis for how this AF6

343
00:20:23.756 --> 00:20:27.456
